headline: Icertis Launches Vera to Power Contract Intelligence with Smarter AI
summary: NEW YORK, September 10, 2025--Icertis today introduced Vera, a smarter AI for contracts that delivers contract intelligence enterprises can trust. Powered by one of the largest repositories of contract data in the world, Icertis Vera reflects the true intent of agreements with unmatched accuracy through deep contextual understanding of the business relationships captured in contracts.
